  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Bellevue is a stylish mountain retreat, sitting in an elevated position above <a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a> centre. The hotel perfectly combines homely <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austrian</a> hospitality with attractive modern facilities. You are conveniently placed just five minutes stroll to the nearest ski lift.</p>
<h2>Wellness</h2>
<p>After a day exploring Obergurgl’s cinematic ski area, you will appreciate the extensive spa facilities that comprise an indoor and outdoor pool, whirlpool, sauna, steam room, relaxation room and treatment area. Take in the unique mountain setting on the hotel's sun terrace, or let off steam in the state of the art gym.  </p>
<h2>Food &amp; drink</h2>
<p>Each morning and evening you can enjoy hearty cuisine that celebrates dishes from across Europe. Hotel Bellevue receives consistently great feedback for its cuisine and attentive service.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p>Younger guests are well accommodated with a hotel kindergarten, play room and games room. There are also great family rooms available sleeping up to five.</p>
<h2>Rooms</h2>
<p>Bedrooms have been recently renovated and are designed with great attention to detail and immaculately kept.</p>]]></description>
