  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Type B1 </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around 18m² and have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Type B3 </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around 45m² and sleep up to four using a double sofa bed in the lounge area. These rooms have a shower and balcony with south facing views.</p>
<p><strong>Type B4 </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around 45m² and sleep up to four using a double sofa bed in the lounge area. These rooms have a bath and balcony with south facing views.</p>
<p><strong>Type B5 </strong>Austrian twin rooms offer the most space at around 48m² and ideal for families of up to five. They have a separate bedroom with Austrian twin beds, lounge area with double and single sofa beds, and also a bath. </p>
<p><strong>Single </strong>rooms are around 15m² with a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>WiFi</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
